  </tr>
</table>
<table border="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td width="12%"><span style="font-family:Arial"><font size="3">where</font>
</span></td>
    <td width="6%"><img border="0" src="../images/6trigf6.jpg" width="23" height="46"></td>
    <td width="82%"><span style="font-family:Arial"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>tells us we are going from the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal">m</b>edium
triangle to the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal">s</b>mall triangle.<o:p>
      &nbsp;
</span></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<table border="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
